892%29.jpg/330px-Liberty_Mutual_-_Headquarters_%2854953357892%29.jpg","wikipediaUrl":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liberty_Mutual","extract":"Liberty Mutual Insurance Company, often referred to as Liberty Mutual Insurance, is an American diversified global insurer and the sixth-largest property and casualty insurer in the world. It ranks 87th on the Fortune 100 list of largest corporations in the United States based on 2024 revenue. Based in Boston, Massachusetts, it employs over 45,000 people in more than 900 locations throughout the world. As of December 31, 2021, Liberty Mutual Insurance had $156.043 billion in consolidated assets, $128.195 billion in consolidated liabilities and $48.2 billion in annual consolidated revenue."},"bbb":{"rating":"A+","accredited":null,"complaintCount":null,"profileUrl":"https://www.bbb.org/us/mi/farmington-hills/profile/insurance-companies/liberty-mutual-0372-90058155/addressId/250896"},"secComplaints":{"count":17,"sample":[{"adsh":"0001524358-26-000004","date":"2026-02-17","filer":"MARRIOTT VACATIONS WORLDWIDE Corp  (VAC)  (CIK 0001524358)","form":"8-K"},{"adsh":"0001524358-26-000004","date":"2026-02-17","filer":"MARRIOTT VACATIONS WORLDWIDE Corp  (VAC)  (CIK 0001524358)","form":"8-K"},{"adsh":"0001140361-25-008453","date":"2025-03-12","filer":"CLECO POWER LLC  (CIK 0000018672)","form":"8-K"}]},"logoUrl":"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Liberty%20Mutual%20logo.svg","logoSource":"wikidata_p154","slug":"liberty-mutual","news":null,"payRatio":null,"deiBadges":null,"animalCerts":null,"products":null,"storeFootprint":null,"recalls":null,"origin":null,"ownership":null,"charity_irs990":null,"firearms_atf_ffl":null,"environment_ejscreen":null,"ownership_wikidata":null,"privacy_hibp_breaches":null,"litigation_courtlistener":{"caseCount24mo":5,"classActionCount":0,"mostRecentCase":"2026-06-01","cases":[{"caseName":"Lockhart v. Liberty Mutual Insurance Company","dateFiled":"2026-06-01","court":"District Court, S.D. Florid